caption: (Translated by Google) It is an economical option in this expensive city. They usually have bathrooms. They have a 6 dollar menu that includes a medium sandwich with a sachet of potatoes plus a soda. All very rich and fast if you are passing through.  (Original) Es una opción económica en esta ciudad tan cara. Suelen tener baños. Tienen un menú de 6 dolares que incluye un sandwich mediano con una bolsita de papas mas una gaseosa. Todo muy rico y rápido si estas de paso.
Closed before the time I went in then got an urgent phone call just step out and when I was going back in he says CLOSED like 5 min early.

Double check your receipts. After several times of coming here. I felt the price was a bit off. This time I asked for the receipt and looked at it. I bought a 6.75 foot long Turkey and got charged with foot long bbq chicken. He went to the tip jar and paid me back my differnce . Business practice like this means this place isn't attracting customers.

Fast! Very fast. I was late to class, this place had a fast line. I took a chance and man I was lucky. Got my Cheese Steak and made it to class just in time. I used my pace card there as well. SAVINGS!!!!
